             was indicted for <rs id="t17831210-57-off314" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17831210-57-off314" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17831210-57-off314" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17831210-57-cd315" type="crimeDate">1st of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-57-off314 t17831210-57-cd315"></join> last, ten yards of black silk lace, value 30 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-57-victim656" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Hilliard
                        <interp inst="t17831210-57-victim656" type="surname" value="Hilliard"></interp>
